<!DOCTYPE html>

<head>
    <title>Log-in Tutorial</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../style/menustyle.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-eOJMYsd53ii+scO/bJGFsiCZc+5NDVN2yr8+0RDqr0Ql0h+rP48ckxlpbzKgwra6" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"
        integrity="sha256-/xUj+3OJU5yExlq6GSYGSHk7tPXikynS7ogEvDej/m4=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="mainnav">
        <h3 id="player-username">{{username}}</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/">Back to Main Menu</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="main-container row mt-5 justify-content-center">

        <div class="card" style="width: 60rem">
            <h2 class="card-title text-center">Log-In Tutorial</h2>
            <div class="card-body">
                <p>When you click on the "Log-In" button, you will be redirected to the Log-In page.</p>
                <p>Here, you are required to enter
                <ul>
                    <li>The e-mail associated with their account.</li>
                    <li>The password for the account.</li>
                </ul>

                <img class="justify-content-center" src="../img/SignInPageImage.jpg" alt="login-tutorial">

                <p>1. The "E-mail address" field. The e-mail must be associated with an account that has already been registered</p>
                <p>2. The "Password" field. It must match the password for the account associated with the e-mail provided above.</p>
                <p>3. The "Submit" button. You press this in order for your details to be verified on the system.</p>
                <br>
                <p>If the entered details have been proven to be valid, you will be logged in, and you will now have access to the Game and Leaderboard pages.</p>

                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-info" href="/tutorial2">Registration Tutorial</a>
                    <a class="btn btn-outline-info" href="/tutorial4">Game Setup Tutorial</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>

</html>